{"tid":2368443,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Inside Cyberpunk 2077's Disastrous Rollout","createTime":"2021-01-16T07:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T03:29:32.000Z","uid":169195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8d1b7f872409db557556381c4375d0ad478bc3f7","tid":2368443,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jasonschreier/status/1350322423170797568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjasonschreier%2Fstatus%2F1350322423170797568&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=c11525a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjasonschreier%2Fstatus%2F1350322423170797568&h=5b99b22a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jasonschreier/status/1350322423170797568</a><br />\n<br />\nSome tidbits that were cut from the piece:<br />\n<br />\n- If you're wondering just how much Cyberpunk 2077 changed over the past decade: well, up until 2016, it was a third-person game. Features that were originally envisioned (wall-running, flying cars, car ambushes) were cut along the way (not atypical in game development)<br />\n<br />\n- And if you're wondering why the police system in Cyberpunk 2077 is so janky: well, it was all done at the last minute. As is evident by the final product, it was unclear to some of the team why they were trying to make both an RPG and a GTA with a fraction of Rockstar's staff<br />\n<br />\nIn conclusion: Cyberpunk was announced eight years ago, but development didn't really start until 2016. In 2018, they had little but a (mostly) fake demo. Most of the staff knew and openly said it wouldn't be ready for release in 2020. But management believed in CD Projekt Magic"},{"pid":"7a803bd996cac39d8b1317d21f56eda92b83c792","tid":2368443,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Er1SyyCXMAIHEOm?format=png&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEr1SyyCXMAIHEOm%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3Dsmall&h=b129892b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90630065dcff988ce726c5b8a88a00a21eff2cb9","tid":2368443,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:33:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4190c61da1aed0d03bb229974303ae8c7526857f","tid":2368443,"uid":140283,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:59:46.000Z","msg":"執咗佢啦 仲話出online版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10e126bf0a11a7c1f7214b79160c5d31bedf87f","tid":2368443,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add7d10468d05f80ae1a1f66e7d4192f757d467e","tid":2368443,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c716e90d76cdba448fb68c54d0c7af9508a1c6d","tid":2368443,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T02:30:23.000Z","msg":"好似話啲dev 本身預2022 先有可能做完"},{"pid":"7dd681ac8c2b614ee2a402296f3e524f64ac814b","tid":2368443,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T02:45:45.000Z","msg":"英文無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f550c3bfdc37c08538c2988b37d195c473dfaa","tid":2368443,"uid":64522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"根本就係Bioware Magic 2.0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb51ac6b043da1f57a58b09ede6d0f3635b9b228","tid":2368443,"uid":5320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T03:16:11.000Z","msg":"高層繼續撥火<img src=\"/a